    <item>
      <title>泰国 Pita 餐厅在十年政治禁令后重返哈佛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/thailand-s-pita-to-return-to-harvard-following-10-year-political-ban-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国著名政治家皮塔·林贾龙拉 (Pita Limjaroenrat) 将重返哈佛大学，在那里他将获得奖学金并分享他在政治动荡时期的经验教训，他的政党在大选中获胜，但在一年后解散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/thailand-s-pita-to-return-to-harvard-following-10-year-political-ban-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
